title: TikTok
description: Short-form mobile videos platform for entertainment and creativity

title: Instagram
description: Photo and video sharing social networking service.Instagram is a visual platform focused on sharing photos, videos, and stories, exploring trends through hashtags, watching reels and live streams, and engaging with influencers, brands, and shopping features.

title: WhatsApp Messenger
description: Simple, reliable, private messaging and calling.WhatsApp is an instant messaging app that allows text, voice, and video chats, supports group conversations, shares media and locations, and ensures secure communication with end-to-end encryption across mobile and desktop devices.

title: Facebook
description: Connect with friends, family and people who share your interests.Facebook is a social networking site that lets people connect with friends and family, post updates, photos, and videos, join groups and events, buy and sell items through the marketplace, and chat via Messenger.

title: Spotify
description: Stream music and podcasts, discover new artists and songs

title: Netflix
description: Watch TV shows and movies recommended just for you

title: YouTube
description: Official YouTube app for watching videos and sharing content.YouTube is a video-sharing platform where users can watch, upload, and share content, follow channels, create playlists, engage through comments and likes, and even earn revenue through monetization

title: Snapchat
description: Fast and fun way to share moments with friends and family

title: Telegram
description: Fast and secure messaging app with cloud sync

title: Zoom
description: Video conferencing, web conferencing, webinars, screen sharing

title: Amazon Shopping
description: Shop millions of products with fast delivery and easy returns

title: Gmail
description: Official Gmail app with secure, organized email.Gmail is an email service by Google that allows users to send, receive, and organize emails efficiently. It offers features like spam filtering, labels, search, and integration with other Google services. Users can attach files, schedule emails, and access their account across devices. Gmail supports both personal and professional communication. It has become one of the most widely used email platforms worldwide.

title: Google Maps
description: Google Maps is a mapping and navigation service that provides detailed maps, directions, and real-time traffic information. Users can explore locations, find businesses, and get turn-by-turn navigation for driving, walking, or public transit. It includes features like street view, satellite imagery, and user reviews. Google Maps helps with trip planning, local discovery, and route optimization. It is widely used for both everyday commuting and travel purposes.

title: Microsoft Teams
description: Microsoft Teams is a collaboration platform for workplaces and educational institutions. It integrates chat, video conferencing, file sharing, and collaborative editing in one space. Users can organize meetings, manage projects, and communicate within teams. Teams supports integration with Microsoft 365 apps for productivity. It streamlines communication and teamwork across organizations.

title: Discord
description: Discord is a communication platform for voice, video, and text chat, popular among gamers and online communities. Users can create servers, join channels, and interact in real-time. It supports screen sharing, live streaming, and integration with other apps. Discord is used for socializing, gaming, education, and hobby communities. It offers both public and private spaces for collaboration and discussion.

title: Uber
description: Uber is a ride-hailing platform that connects passengers with drivers through a mobile app. It offers various services including UberX, UberPool, and food delivery via Uber Eats. Users can track rides in real-time and pay through the app. The platform provides convenience, safety features, and fare transparency. Uber has transformed urban transportation and delivery services globally.

title: PayPal
description: PayPal is an online payment platform that allows users to send, receive, and manage money securely. It supports online shopping, money transfers, and linking bank accounts or cards. Businesses and individuals can use it for transactions worldwide. PayPal offers buyer and seller protection to ensure safe payments. It is widely used for e-commerce, subscriptions, and digital services.

title: Twitter
description: Follow your interests and join conversations.Twitter is a microblogging platform where users share short messages called tweets, follow others for real-time updates, use hashtags to join trending discussions, and interact through retweets, likes, and direct messages.

title: LinkedIn
description: Professional networking and job search platform.LinkedIn is a professional networking platform designed for career development and business connections. Users create profiles showcasing their skills, experience, and achievements. It allows connecting with colleagues, recruiters, and industry professionals, and sharing posts or articles. LinkedIn offers job listings, company pages, and professional learning courses. It serves as a hub for networking, personal branding, and industry insights.

title: Pinterest
description: Pinterest is a visual discovery platform where users can find and save ideas for projects, fashion, recipes, home decor, and more. People create boards to organize their favorite images, follow others for inspiration, and explore trending topics. It allows sharing of pins, ideas, and links to external websites. Businesses use it for marketing and driving traffic to their content. Pinterest combines creativity and planning, making it popular for hobbies, DIY projects, and lifestyle inspiration.
